---
title: Grilled Sausage Burgers with Smoky Aioli and Spiced Wedges
description: Juicy sausage burgers are on the grill tonight! These delicious handhelds are stuffed with roasted red peppers and slathered with garlicky paprika aioli for a burger you won't soon forget!
